ributed renewable energy and storage systems were\nidentified as unprofitable for the community. Occupant behavior was\nparticularly exposed as the leading uncertainty factor impacting energy\ncommunity planning. This demonstrates the relevance and value of our approach\nin connecting occupants to cities for improved, and more resilient, urban\nenergy planning strategies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Mar 2023 10:16:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-07"}
